{"tid":749464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］蔣介石棺慘遭被潑漆","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T07:37:54.000Z","uid":57214,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47dcbca6b456344497176b3f56edef1296b07b7f","tid":749464,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"青年今晨襲「中正廟」砸蔣銅像 兩人遭移送派出所<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5abd8f50e17ba366312a1158/t/5b514e758a922d1f461e64cd/1532055176715/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5abd8f50e17ba366312a1158%2Ft%2F5b514e758a922d1f461e64cd%2F1532055176715%2F&h=6cd70b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨派青年團體「蠻番島嶼社」今年228在慈湖對蔣介石棺柩潑漆，遭桃園檢方起訴，預計今（20日）下午將開庭審理。今晨，他們選擇前往中正紀念堂，突破封鎖，對禮堂中的蔣介石銅像砸紅漆蛋抗議，最終有兩名青年遭移送仁愛派出所。<br />\n<br />\n據民報報導，潑漆當下，中正紀念堂的駐衛警有上前阻止，多名遊客則拿起手機、相機拍照。潑漆的獨派青年最後拉起布條，高喊「去除支那權威，創建台灣共和」等口號。而《讀報》掌握的獨家消息指出，目前已有2人遭移送仁愛派出所。<br />\n<br />\n發動潑漆行動的「蠻番島嶼社」表示，執政的民進黨應盡速落實《促進轉型正義條例》中「清除威權象徵、保存不義遺址」的規定，否則反抗不會停止。<br />\n<br />\n「蠻番島嶼社」認為，轉型正義所訴求的和解，並非是向反動的保守勢力妥協，也不是為了「不造成對立」而便宜地「維持現狀」。他們主張，真正的和解，是向未來的下一代承諾一個再也不會有獨裁者崇拜，實實在在自由民主獨立的新國度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dopost.com/articles-3/20180720-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dopost.com%2Farticles-3%2F20180720-3&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w0zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bb7e8ac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dopost.com/articles-3/20180720-3</a>"},{"pid":"dc0b301974d3aa4f6eede57b31d760e0cb282f13","tid":749464,"uid":57214,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去除支那權威，創建台灣共和</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abca523577c47beb816fc51d0777500aace6a10","tid":749464,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7a743d4331bdd74476c39fb533d3aac9d2ab832","tid":749464,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2abca523577c47beb816fc51d0777500aace6a10","tid":749464,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"國父緊係搵李登輝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b90833d89363f2182f5468827943831f18c19b4","tid":749464,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a743d4331bdd74476c39fb533d3aac9d2ab832","tid":749464,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2abca523577c47beb816fc51d0777500aace6a10","tid":749464,"uid":132038,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"國父緊係搵李登輝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c447462ac8bdb5bf94e915e60739359ca31707","tid":749464,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82741493ea6801f630c160fcc8f5157810fc8465","tid":749464,"uid"